Note: Participant expresses how difficult it is to view reels as sun is shining brightly into car
Participant says they can see external objects in display while watching videos, like car license plates and moving cars — distracting
Participant describes their susceptibility to motion sickness as a bit more than the average person but nothing major

Participant notices they are more accustomed to hand gestures than earlier sessions and finds that neural band is more responsive at this point
When asked if participant is aware of what’s happening on the road, they responded with “only when I am not focusing on the reels that I’m watching” in the MR glasses display
